snippet.title: Yoostar 2: In the Movies [PEGI 12] - Game Trailer
snippet.description: Star in real Hollywood blockbusters with Yoostar 2: In the Movies for Kinect! With 80 iconic scenes available on launch and hundreds more available online, Yoostar 2 puts you in the movies! Look out for the game on 11th April!
